Changes when moving to a KDE4-based distribution (debian >= squeeze or
ubuntu >= intrepid):

Always:

- Replace "kpdf" with "xpdf | okular" in regina-normal's recommends.

If khelpcenter4 doesn't work:

- Big warning in regina-normal.README.Debian
- Remove khelpcenter from regina-normal's recommends.

If khelpcenter4 does work:

- Replace khelpcenter with khelpcenter4 in regina-normal's recommends.

If kfmclient doesn't work:

- Change "konqueror" to "konqueror | www-browser" in regina-normal-doc's
  recommends.
- Remove konqueror from regina-normal's suggestions.

